'),(57,53,27,2,'black 2 draft','2025-06-14 12:03:53','2025-06-14 12:03:53'),(58,54,24,5,'The New Resident\n---------------------------------------\nWeeks passed. Room Five was sealed again.\n\nUntil the new student, Alex, arrived.\n\nHe heard about the stories, the disappearances, and the rumors. But he didn’t care. He liked danger. He liked breaking rules.\n\nOne night, he wandered the halls. He found the door. It looked just like any other now. Fresh paint. New lock. But something about it pulled at him.\n\nAs he leaned close, he heard it—barely audible, a girl’s voice:\n\n“Help me…”\n\nHe reached for the knob.\n\nBehind the door, in the mirror, Lena smiled.\n\nSo did the others.','2025-06-28 19:58:03','2025-06-28 19:58:03');
